{"tid":1785036,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"ABC 美國三城市 關注中國中車涉童工","createTime":"2019-12-16T05:53:59.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-16T16:52:37.000Z","uid":165683,"like":9,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"91ef94b0ccc260046b17077098d6965387599cac","tid":1785036,"uid":165683,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-16T05:53:59.000Z","msg":"美國三個城市洛杉磯、芝加哥及費城的捷運當局，準備向為他們生產地鐵及火車車廂的「中國中車」公司提出質詢，要求提供製造列車零部件的來源資料。<br />\n<br />\n美國全國廣播公司花了一年時間，進行調查報道，發現非洲一家生產列車零部件的公司，聘用廉價童工，年齡最小的童工只有4歲。報道相信「中國中車」公司亦有購入這家非洲公司的零部件。<br />\n<br />\n「中國中車」在芝加哥的子公司「中國中車四方美國」發表聲明，表示他們主要在中國生產列車外殻，零件是列車運到美國後才裝配，而他們購買的大部分零件都是來自美國的供應商，聲明強調，期望供應商能以有尊嚴的方式善待自己的員工。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1497827-20191216.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1497827-20191216.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=dVEf9brN%2BTtwApumOSMW7n9Z9R%2B5WvgLevJIGZbvuGo%3D&h=9e46a0e0\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1497827-20191216.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=df5e7fc1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1497827-20191216.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a>"},{"pid":"efe5f42844f377056733dd659207b2d7a91cc2a0","tid":1785036,"uid":251769,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-16T05:56:13.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">請各位喺出post前貼多張日程表or文宣</span></span><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">咁文宣組就冇咁忙啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/sdw2RCH.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fsdw2RCH.jpg&h=8da8b8c7&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ja88Na2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fja88Na2.jpg&h=543efee6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/WmRJ7hx.jpg